reviewText: Pure campy over-the-top humor, with a "who's who" cast.
parts were cut out from original but it was OK

Hypocrites beware! Stella is on the loose. This is a terrific movie. She let those who were calling her a tramp know they were no better than she. I love this movie. From beginning to the end it's really good. She showed them all.
I really enjoyed this movie when it was in the theater. Barbara Eden and the other cast members are great!
